---
title: Miso Apricot Chicken with Garlic Ginger Rice & Zesty Carrots
description: No need to be chicken about making this delicious, saucy meal. Crispy chicken cutlets are drizzled with an umami-packed sauce of apricot jam, miso broth, lime juice, and butter. On the side, there’s fluffy, aromatic ginger rice, plus roasted carrots tossed with lime zest. Talk about a weeknight dinner worth hatching out!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/622610b649990671902672e3-17151a87.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/miso-apricot-chicken-622610b649990671902672e3-6d2eca5e.pdf
author: HelloFresh
time required: 40 minutes
servings: 2
course: main course
